ymbole de persuasion.  \t"}},"en":{"name":"Symbol Of Persuasion","link":"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/magic/all-spells/S/Symbol Of Persuasion","details":{"school":"<strong>School </strong>enchantment(charm)[mind-affecting];","level":"<strong>Level </strong>cleric 6, sorcerer/wizard 6, witch 6","castTime":"<strong>Casting Time </strong>10 minutes","components":"<strong>Components </strong>V, S, M (mercury and phosphorus, plus powdered diamond and opal worth a total of 5,000 gp)","range":"<strong>Range </strong>0 ft.; see text","target":"<strong>Effect </strong>one symbol","duration":"<strong>Duration </strong>see text","save":"<strong>Saving Throw </strong>Will negates;","spellResistance":"<strong>SR </strong>yes","description":"<strong>Description </strong>  This spell functions like symbol of death, except that all creatures  within the radius of a symbol of persuasion instead become charmed by  the caster (as the charm monster spell) for 1 hour per caster level.    Unlike symbol of death, symbol of persuasion has no hit point limit;  once triggered, a symbol of persuasion simply remains active for 10  minutes per caster level.   Note: Magic traps such as symbol of  persuasion are hard to detect and disable. A rogue (only) can use the  Perception skill to find a symbol of persuasion and Disable Device to  thwart it. The DC in each case is 25 + spell level, or 31 for symbol of  persuasion.   "}}},{"fr":{"name":"Symbole de sommeil","link":"https://www.pathfinder-fr.org/Wiki/Pathfinder-RPG.Symbole%20de%20sommeil.ashx","details":{"target":"<strong>Cible</strong> 1 symbole ","school":"<strong>École</strong> Enchantement (coercition) [mental] ; ","level":"<strong>Niveau</strong> Hyp 5, Ens/Mag 5, Occ 4, Prê 5, Sor 5 ","castTime":"<strong>Temps d'incantation</strong> 10 minutes ","components":"<strong>Composantes</strong> V, G, M (mercure et phosphore, plus un diamant et une opale en poudre (1 000 po au total)) ","range":"<strong>Portée</strong> 0 m (voir description) ","spel